  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jet Fighters with Friends 2</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UFOs are attacking Paris, Go get 'em!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single Player OR Multiplayer Jet Fighter Game with A.I. UFO Bots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvP or COOP.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly different types of Jets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Guns and Missiles to defeat them to win !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb Your way to the top, shoot and hunt enemies in a multiplayer match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be challenged to determine the best pilot who destroys the other jet fighters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take Your Jet to new heights, the sky is NO Limit !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >** You need a Solid & Fast Internet Connection for best results. **</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* This game is part of the \"Jets\" mini-series event from Archor Games, be sure to check it out on Steam! *</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jet Fighters with Friends 2</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UFOs are attacking Paris, Go get 'em!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single Player OR Multiplayer Jet Fighter Game with A.I. UFO Bots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvP or COOP.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly different types of Jets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Guns and Missiles to defeat them to win !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb Your way to the top, shoot and hunt enemies in a multiplayer match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be challenged to determine the best pilot who destroys the other jet fighters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take Your Jet to new heights, the sky is NO Limit !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >** You need a Solid & Fast Internet Connection for best results. **</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* This game is part of the \"Jets\" mini-series event from Archor Games, be sure to check it out on Steam! *</p>",
